# Install-gcloud-sdk

https://cloud.google.com/sdk/docs/quickstart


## Install on Mac

```
curl https://dl.google.com/dl/cloudsdk/channels/rapid/downloads/google-cloud-sdk-371.0.0-darwin-x86_64.tar.gz -o gcloud-sdk.tar.gz
tar -xf gcloud-sdk.tar.gz
./google-cloud-sdk/install.sh
source ~/.bash_profile 
```

### Setup & Configure the gcloud project 

`gcloud init`

### If you have service account with access key created then you can also use 

`gcloud auth activate-service-account <client_email-given-inside-keyfile> --key-file=<location-of-key-file>.json`